import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import '../style.css'
import {
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  CssBaseline,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Button,
} from '@mui/material';

const Navbar = ({ logout, token }) => {
  return (
      <AppBar position='static'>
        <CssBaseline>
          <Toolbar>
            <Grid container>
              <Typography 
              type="title"
              style={{fontSize:'1.75rem'}}>
                Stranger's Things
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid container
              display="flex"
              justifyContent="flex-end"
              alignItems="flex-end">
                <Typography>
                  <Link to='/'><Button
                    style={{
                      margin: '.10rem',
                      color: 'white',
                      backgroundColor: 'red'
                    }}>
                    Home
                  </Button></Link>
                  <Link to='/posts'><Button
                    style={{
                      margin: '.10rem',
                      color: 'white',
                      backgroundColor: 'red'
                    }}>
                    Posts
                  </Button></Link>
                  {
                    token ? (
                      <>
                        <Link to='/profile'><Button
                          style={{
                            margin: '.10rem',
                            color: 'white',
                            backgroundColor: 'red'
                          }}>
                          Profile
                        </Button></Link>
                        <Link to='/' onClick={() => logout()}><Button
                          style={{
                            margin: '.10rem',
                            color: 'white',
                            backgroundColor: 'red'
                          }}>
                          Logout
                        </Button></Link>
                      </>
                    ) : (
                      <>
                        <Link to='/register'><Button
                          style={{
                            margin: '.10rem',
                            color: 'white',
                            backgroundColor: 'red'
                          }}>
                          New Account
                        </Button></Link>
                        <Link to='/login'><Button
                          style={{
                            margin: '.10rem',
                            color: 'white',
                            backgroundColor: 'red'
                          }}>
                          Sign In
                        </Button></Link>
                      </>
                    )
                  }
                </Typography>
            </Grid>
          </Toolbar>
        </CssBaseline>
      </AppBar>
  )

}

export default Navbar;
